data.description: You will know you have come home when you walk into this elegant 1 level brick home with lots of upgrades * 4 large bedrooms with large living room and formal dining room. A beautiful kitchen, a breakfast nook and breakfast bars * Granite countertops *Built in desk * Nice pantry * Under counter lighting *  A large Master Suite with trey ceiling's, crown molding and a master bath you dream about. * Open floor plan * this home is ideal for any family. with a large deck for entertaining or relaxing overlooking a fenced-in back yard with a double lot and a creek for you enjoyment.  There will be plenty of room for a growing family to make many memories.
